      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASTON ALARM (2) was prominent throughout when winning in one of the fastest times of the card two back but could manage only midfield last time when finished 6th and beaten 5.5 lengths at Q Lakeside (22.62). The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Has ability and looks hard to stop. BUNDY ALL GO (1) is rarely out of the finish, recording nine places from 20 starts. Finished second (20.00) at this track last time making it five minors on end. Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in three starts. Expected to be in the finish again. DENIM BEACH (7) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (20.45) at this track behind Satoshi in a P5. Settled off speed and worked to the line nicely. Expected to feature again. HARA'S MAX (5) was out of the money at this circuit last start but can bounce back.",
